headline: MEDIA ALERT: LEADERS GATHER AT GROUNDBREAKERS 2025
summary: Prologis presents its annual thought leadership forum, GROUNDBREAKERS™ 2025, a one‑day event that brings together business leaders, policymakers and innovators on major issues shaping the global supply chain. At a time when geopolitical and trade policy changes are resetting business strategies, GROUNDBREAKERS will explore top-of-mind topics critical to the movement of goods and growth of business.
